tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE CuisineReport (
    cuisine_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    cuisine_name VARCHAR(255),
    total_sales DECIMAL(10, 2),
    total_expenses DECIMAL(10, 2),
    profit DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE Cuisines (
 cuisine_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 cuisine_name TEXT,
 country TEXT,
 sales_data DECIMAL,
 expenses DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE Reports (
 report_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 date DATE,
 cuisine_id UUID,
 profitability DECIMAL,
 FOREIGN KEY (cuisine_id) REFERENCES Cuisines(cuisine_id)
)

CREATE TABLE CuisineExpenses (
    cuisine_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    ingredient_cost DECIMAL(10, 2),
    labor_cost DECIMAL(10, 2),
    rent_cost DECIMAL(10, 2),
    year INT
);

CREATE TABLE CuisineProfitability (
    cuisine_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    cuisine_type VARCHAR(255),
    total_sales DECIMAL(10, 2),
    total_expenses DECIMAL(10, 2),
    net_profit DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE Reports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    report_name VARCHAR(255),
    report_date DATE,
    cuisine_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (cuisine_id) REFERENCES CuisineProfitability(cuisine_id)
);

CREATE TABLE cuisine_expenses (
    expense_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    cuisine_id INT NOT NULL,
    expense_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    expense_amount DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    expense_date DATE NOT NULL
);
